    <item>
      <title>台湾最高法院驳回扩大立法权的关键法案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/taiwan-s-top-court-rejects-key-laws-expanding-legislative-powers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾最高法院裁定扩大立法者权力的关键法律变化违宪，这一判决可能使赖清德总统更容易治理处于中美紧张局势中心的群岛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/taiwan-s-top-court-rejects-key-laws-expanding-legislative-powers</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 08:32:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨承诺加强与印度的贸易以遏制中国的主导地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/scholz-pledges-stronger-trade-with-india-to-curb-china-dominance</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨呼吁进一步实现国家贸易多元化，他希望减少德国经济对中国的依赖，转而依赖印度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/scholz-pledges-stronger-trade-with-india-to-curb-china-dominance</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 25 Oct 2024 07:40:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中印开始从边境摩擦点撤军</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/china-india-start-removing-troops-from-border-friction-points</link>
      <description><![CDATA[几天前，中印两国领导人举行会晤，随后两国军队开始从喜马拉雅山争议边界剩下的两个摩擦点撤军。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-25/china-india-start-removing-troops-from-border-friction-points</guid>
